data.description: Super sharp and functional 2011 built Beazer home in West Lancaster! This great 4 bedroom floorplan features 1 bedroom and full bath downstairs with a modern, open floorplan. The large and open great room is open to the dining area and kitchen with large island. The granite counters and island provide so much space in the kitchen! The laundry room is conveniently located off the kitchen. Upstairs there are 3 more bedrooms plus a great loft, and a large master suite with dual vanities, separate tub and shower and a nice walk in closet. Fully landscaped front and rear, this home features a spacious covered patio, large grassy yard in the back, and is also updated with water efficient xeriscape in the front. The recently added additional cement parking area and gated RV access provides plenty of room for your RV, trailer, boat or whatever you can imagine! Conveniently located close to schools and shopping, this is a great home. Schedule a showing today!
